oopener noreferrer\">Facebook<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/smiledirectclub\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Twitter<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.snapchat.com\/add\/smiledirectclub\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Snapchat<\/a>,\u00a0and more. Let&#8217;s be friends.<\/p>\n<h3><b>5. Start practicing good habits.<\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Once you start wearing your aligners, you&#8217;ll want to <a href=\"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/6-tips-your-biggest-dental-hygiene-questions\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">brush and floss your teeth<\/a> after every meal or snack. If you&#8217;re not a regular flosser, start small by getting into the habit of flossing every day when you brush your teeth before leaving the house or going to bed.<span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>6. Reach out to us with any questions.<\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>We&#8217;re here for you. Our Customer Care team is available via chat, email, phone, video chat, and social media 24\/7 to answer any questions you might have. <a href=\"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/doctors-behind-your-smile\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Dental team<\/a> is also here to talk you through anything more clinical.\u00a0Don&#8217;t be shy. If you&#8217;ve got questions, we&#8217;ve got answers.\u00a0<span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><b>7. Take a &#8220;before&#8221; picture,<\/b><\/h3>\n<p>It&#8217;s always good to mark your starting point. Having this picture can help keep you motivated and help you to see how much your teeth are moving!<\/p>\n<h3><b>8. Mark your calendar to order retainers.<\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Another thing you can do while you&#8217;re waiting for your aligners is mark your calendar to order <a href=\"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/dont-forget-your-retainers\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">retainers<\/a>. We recommend ordering retainers 4-5 weeks before treatment is complete to ensure they arrive in time, so mark your calendar now so you don&#8217;t forget later. You&#8217;ll want to have your retainers right when you finish your last set of aligners to preserve your beautiful new smile.<\/p>\n<p>Welcome to the Club. We can&#8217;t wait to see that new grin.<span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.smiledirectclub.com\/smile_assessment\">\t<p style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/www.pages03.net\/smiledirectclub\/retainers\" class=\"btn btn--purple\">\r\n\t\t\tOrder Retainers\t\t<\/a>\r\n\t<\/p>\r\n\t<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Get\u00a0ready to start straightening!\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":20,"featured_media":3154,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[875,869],"tags":[172,262,17,499,484,498,497],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1516"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/20"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blogorigin.wpengine.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1516"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href"